<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mon Compte - EcoNutri</title>
    
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Notre CSS personnalisé -->
    <link href="{{ asset('styles/home.css') }}" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        .account-section {
            padding: 100px 0 50px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .account-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            border: none;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .account-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
        }
        
        .profile-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            padding-bottom: 2rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f1f3f4;
        }
        
        .profile-avatar {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--accent-color));
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            color: white;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }
        
        .profile-header h1 {
            color: var(--text-dark);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .profile-header .text-muted {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        
        .info-item {
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #ffffff 100%);
            border-radius: 15px;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .info-item:hover {
            transform: translateX(5px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .info-value {
            color: var(--text-dark);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .btn-home {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 35px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            border: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .btn-home:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .objectif-badge {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-color), #28a745);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.3);
        }
        
        .section-title {
            color: var(--text-dark);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }
        
        .section-title i {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }
        
        .empty-state {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }
        
        .empty-state i {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #dee2e6;
        }
        
        .nav-link.active {
            color: var(--primary-color) !important;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
     


        /* Modern Orders Section */
.orders-section {
    margin-top: 2rem;
}

.order-card-modern {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.order-card-modern::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 4px;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--accent-color));
}

.order-card-modern:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
}

.order-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f8f9fa;
}

.order-info {
    flex: 1;
}

.order-number {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}

.order-date {
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.order-status-badge {
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.status-pending {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3cd, #ffc107);
    color: #856404;
}

.status-confirmed {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #cce7ff, #17a2b8);
    color: #004085;
}

.status-delivered {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4edda, #28a745);
    color: #155724;
}

.status-cancelled {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8d7da, #dc3545);
    color: #721c24;
}

.order-details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
}

.order-total {
    text-align: right;
}

.order-amount {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}

.order-items {
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.order-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #f8f9fa;
}

.btn-order-details {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(107, 167, 92, 0.3);
}

.btn-order-details:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(107, 167, 92, 0.4);
    color: white;
}

.btn-order-track {
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
    color: var(--primary-color);
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
}

.btn-order-track:hover {
    background: var(--primary-color);
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
}

/* Empty State Modern */
.empty-state-modern {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #ffffff);
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 2px dashed #dee2e6;
}

.empty-state-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--accent-color));
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    color: white;
    font-size: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}

.empty-state-modern h4 {
    color: var(--text-dark);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.empty-state-modern p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 400px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
}

/* Orders List Container */
.orders-list-modern {
    max-height: 600px;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding-right: 10px;
}

.orders-list-modern::-webkit-scrollbar {
    width: 6px;
}

.orders-list-modern::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
    background: #f1f1f1;
    border-radius: 10px;
}

.orders-list-modern::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--accent-color));
    border-radius: 10px;
}

/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .order-header {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
    }
    
    .order-details {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    .order-actions {
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    
    .order-status-badge {
        align-self: flex-start;
    }
}

    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light fixed-top">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="{{ path('app_home') }}">
                <i class="fas fa-leaf me-2"></i>EcoNutri
            </a>
            
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_home') }}">Accueil</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_home') }}#about">À Propos</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                        <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" id="productsDropdown" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
                            Produits
                        </a>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                            {% for cat in get_categories() %}
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="{{ path('app_category', {id: cat.id}) }}">{{ cat.name }}</a></li>
                            {% endfor %}
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#">Conseils</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#">Réclamation</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                
                <div class="navbar-nav">
                    {% if app.user %}
                        <!-- Icône Mon Compte (actif) -->
                        <a class="nav-link active" href="{{ path('app_account') }}" title="Mon Compte">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-circle fa-lg"></i>
                        </a>
                        <!-- Icône Déconnexion -->
                        <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_logout') }}" title="Déconnexion">
                            <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i>
                        </a>
                    {% else %}
                        <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_login') }}">
                            <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt me-1"></i>Connexion
                        </a>
                        <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_register') }}">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-plus me-1"></i>Inscription
                        </a>
                    {% endif %}
                    <!-- Icône Panier -->
                    <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_cart_index') }}" title="Panier">
                        <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i>
                        <span class="badge bg-success">0</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Espace Personnel -->
    <section class="account-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="account-card">
                <!-- En-tête du profil -->
                <div class="profile-header">
                    <div class="profile-avatar">
                        <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h1>{{ user.prenom }} {{ user.nom }}</h1>
                    <p class="text-muted">{{ user.email }}</p>
                    
                    <!-- Bouton retour accueil -->
                    <a href="{{ path('app_home') }}" class="btn-home">
                        <i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>
                        Retour à l'accueil
                    </a>
                </div>

                <!-- Informations personnelles -->
                <h3 class="section-title">
                    <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                    Informations Personnelles
                </h3>
                
                <div class="info-grid">
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="info-label">Genre</div>
                        <div class="info-value">{{ user.genre ?? 'Non spécifié' }}</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="info-label">Téléphone</div>
                        <div class="info-value">{{ user.telephone ?? 'Non spécifié' }}</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="info-label">Taille</div>
                        <div class="info-value">{{ user.taille ? user.taille ~ ' cm' : 'Non spécifié' }}</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="info-label">Poids</div>
                        <div class="info-value">{{ user.poids ? user.poids ~ ' kg' : 'Non spécifié' }}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Objectif -->
                <div class="info-item mb-3">
                    <div class="info-label">Objectif de santé</div>
                    <div class="info-value">
                        {% if user.objectif %}
                            <span class="objectif-badge">{{ user.objectif }}</span>
                        {% else %}
                            <span class="text-muted">Non spécifié</span>
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Adresse -->
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Adresse</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{ user.adresse ?? 'Non spécifiée' }}</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Historique des commandes -->
<div class="account-card">
    <h3 class="section-title">
        <i class="fas fa-shopping-bag"></i>
        Mes Commandes
    </h3>
    
    {% if orders is not empty %}
        <div class="orders-list-modern">
            {% for order in orders %}
            <div class="order-card-modern">
                <div class="order-header">
                    <div class="order-info">
                        <div class="order-number">Commande #{{ order.id }}</div>
                        <div class="order-date">{{ order.createdAt|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }}</div>
                    </div>
                    <span class="order-status-badge 
                        {% if order.status == 'pending' %}status-pending
                        {% elseif order.status == 'confirmed' %}status-confirmed
                        {% elseif order.status == 'delivered' %}status-delivered
                        {% else %}status-cancelled{% endif %}">
                        {{ order.status == 'pending' ? 'En attente' : 
                           order.status == 'confirmed' ? 'Confirmée' : 
                           order.status == 'delivered' ? 'Livrée' : 
                           'Annulée' }}
                    </span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="order-details">
                    <div class="order-items">
                        {{ order.orderItems|length }} produit(s)
                    </div>
                    <div class="order-total">
                        <div class="order-amount">{{ order.grandTotal }} TND</div>
                        <div class="order-shipping">Livraison incluse</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="order-actions">
                    <a href="{{ path('app_order_details', {'id': order.id}) }}" class="btn-order-details">
                        <i class="fas fa-eye me-1"></i>Détails
                    </a>
                    {% if order.status == 'confirmed' or order.status == 'delivered' %}
                    <a href="#" class="btn-order-track">
                        <i class="fas fa-truck me-1"></i>Suivi
                    </a>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    {% else %}
        <div class="empty-state-modern">
            <div class="empty-state-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-box-open"></i>
            </div>
            <h4>Aucune commande pour le moment</h4>
            <p>Votre historique de commandes apparaîtra ici après vos premiers achats chez EcoNutri.</p>
            <a href="{{ path('app_home') }}#categories" class="btn-home">
                <i class="fas fa-shopping-basket me-2"></i>
                Découvrir nos produits
            </a>
        </div>
    {% endif %}
</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <p>&copy; 2025 EcoNutri. Tous droits réservés.</p>
            <div class="mt-3">
                <a href="#" class="text-white me-3"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="text-white me-3"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="text-white me-3"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>


</html>